1
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,450
Drink it.

2
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:07,200
Don't waste the panacea I worked so hard to gather.

3
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:07,840
Thank you.

4
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:18,420
This jade pendant of yours

5
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,240
is quite unique.

6
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,100
It must have quite a story.

7
00:01:22,880 --> 00:01:25,410
Stop looking at things you shouldn't look at.

8
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,840
Marquis Zhenbei's Tiger Tally.

9
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,770
The Xiao family.

10
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,289
Who exactly are you?

11
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:40,000
I am Ren Jiuxiao.

12
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:43,880
I am just a merchant running errands for noblemen.

13
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,600
This thing

14
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:47,680
was given to me by the Xiao family

15
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,100
when I worked for them.

16
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,880
You don't believe me?

17
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,000
Then kill me.

18
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,000
Kill me,

19
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:56,960
and you'll never find out

20
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,759
the truth about the Duke's case.

21
00:01:58,800 --> 00:01:59,600
As expected,

22
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,160
you're coming for me.

23
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,560
Eldest Miss Yan,

24
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,280
who in this capital doesn't know

25
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:12,480
Yan Qingshu, the eldest legitimate daughter of the Duke's estate?

26
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:15,120
You were framed by your stepmother and stepsister,

27
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,079
ruined and driven out of the house.

28
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:18,610
And in this deserted place,

29
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,200
wearing a wedding dress,

30
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,079
it's not hard to recognize you.

31
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:23,010
You know my father's whereabouts?

32
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:25,720
I only heard about it.

33
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,079
If you want to return to Jingdu

34
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,320
to settle old scores,

35
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,120
I can keep you safe.

36
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:36,560
Consider it repaying you for saving my life.

37
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:39,600
Everyone in Jingdu knows

38
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:44,280
the Duke and Marquis Zhenbei have been political enemies for years.

39
00:02:44,640 --> 00:02:46,370
You worked for the Xiao family.

40
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,020
Why are you helping me?

41
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,160
Speak. What are your intentions?

42
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:53,260
Naturally, I desire your breathtaking beauty.

43
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,040
Miss Yan, you are a smart person.

44
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,530
Instead of being suspicious here,

45
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,930
why don't we cooperate sincerely?

46
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,720
Our wishes can be fulfilled together.

47
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:05,680
Cooperate?

48
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,500
Are you worthy?

49
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,690
The road to revenge is long.

50
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:19,400
Without gold and silver paving the way,

51
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:22,160
I'm afraid it will be hard to move a single step.

52
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,520
Information, connections,

53
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,079
wealth, and manpower,

54
00:03:26,920 --> 00:03:27,780
I have them all.

55
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:32,079
Cooperating with me

56
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:33,560
is the most

57
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,640
advantageous for you.

58
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,340
How about this?

59
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:43,280
I'll give you a fine restaurant in the capital

60
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,200
as your base.

61
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:46,800
What do you think?

62
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,680
Mr. Ren is so generous.

63
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,320
This is not repaying a favor.

64
00:03:50,320 --> 00:03:51,880
This is clearly bribery.

65
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,840
I have shown my sincerity.

66
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,320
Next,

67
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:58,300
