68
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,159
Qingshu.

69
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,200
Yuheng.

70
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:49,040
I missed you.

71
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,280
Did you miss me?

72
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,360
Yes.

73
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,400
I missed you too.

74
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,640
