81
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,480
Yan Qingshu.

82
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:25,400
I just want to take back what belongs to me.

83
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,560
Yan Mingli.

84
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:30,880
Why

85
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,040
