91
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,080
and be a heartless man who abandons me?

92
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:45,720
Shut up!

93
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:47,760
Put your clothes on quickly.

94
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:48,520
Just now,

95
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:52,440
it was just me losing control because I was drunk.

96
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:53,640
It was a huge mistake.

97
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,360
A huge mistake?

98
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:58,680
Then,

99
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,920
you and King Ling teamed up

100
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:03,120
to set up a private workshop.

101
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,440
Melting down copper coins,

102
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,440
forging weapons,

103
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,000
secretly colluding with Beidi

104
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,320
to commit treason,

105
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:12,280
and finally laying the blame for this monstrous crime of rebellion

106
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:14,320
entirely on my father.

107
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,920
Every single one of these acts

108
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,840
is a grave crime punishable by the execution of nine generations

109
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:23,040
and death by a thousand cuts.

110
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,240
You...

111
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:25,520
You...

112
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,240
How did you know this?

113
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:30,610
I overheard it when passing by your study.

114
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,940
Don't panic, Brother Yuheng.

115
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,180
As long as you are willing to marry me,

116
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:41,240
we will be husband and wife, united as one.

117
00:07:41,960 --> 00:07:44,760
We share the same glory and the same loss.

118
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,640
Your secrets will be my secrets.

119
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:50,680
I will certainly keep my mouth shut.

120
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,320
Not only that,

121
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,440
I will also give you a great gift.

122
00:07:56,320 --> 00:08:00,000
A great gift you have always dreamed of.

123
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:02,760
What great gift?

124
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:05,080
Heishui Valley's

125
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,800
iron mine map.

126
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,960
Jingdu is just ahead.

127
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:39,080
I promised you

128
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,760
to keep you safe on this journey.

129
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,400
So don't worry.

130
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,290
I won't let you die halfway.

131
00:08:47,560 --> 00:08:48,420
I will remember

132
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,010
your kindness in escorting me.

133
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,000
Yan Qingshu.

134
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:58,420
