154
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,890
Stop being mysterious.

155
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:14,850
Tell us quickly.

156
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,280
I heard that

157
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:21,760
high-ranking court officials have secretly set up a workshop deep in the cave

158
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:23,600
