181
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:19,200
and I'll help you manage Zhuque Pavilion

182
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:22,960
to gather the most valuable gossip in the capital.

183
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:27,760
Deal.

184
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:31,080
Deal.

185
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,440
Miss,

186
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:37,000
