193
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:54,840
Are you really going to search for news of the master here?

194
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,800
I don't think

195
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:57,640
this is a safe place.

196
00:11:59,000 --> 00:11:59,600
Sanniang.

197
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,400
Everyone has

198
00:12:02,760 --> 00:12:03,840
