201
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,560
Win through danger.

202
00:12:10,920 --> 00:12:12,050
Find truth in chaos.

203
00:12:12,280 --> 00:12:12,800
This

204
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:14,400
